trans-unit.source: An inline flow content element that causes a line break to occur in flow content.
trans-unit.target: 유동 콘텐츠 내에 줄 바꿈이 발생 시키는 인라인 유동 콘텐츠 요소

trans-unit.source: Use LineBreak to start a new line of text.
trans-unit.target: LineBreak를 사용 하 여 텍스트의 새 줄을 시작 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Unlike other <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Inline> objects, LineBreak does not allow child elements.
trans-unit.target: 다른 달리 <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Inline>개체 LineBreak 자식 요소 허용 하지 않습니다.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.Inline>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new, default instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.LineBreak"></xref> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.LineBreak"></xref> class, and inserts the new <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.LineBreak"></xref> at a specified position.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.LineBreak"> </xref> 클래스를 삽입 하는 새 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.LineBreak"> </xref> 지정된 된 위치에 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TextPointer"></xref> specifying an insertion position at which to insert the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.LineBreak"></xref> element after it is created, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> for no automatic insertion.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TextPointer"> </xref> 을 삽입할 삽입 위치를 지정 하는 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.LineBreak"> </xref> 요소를 만든 후 또는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> 입니다.
